16 NID_crl_number, 0, ASN1_ITEM_ref(ASN1_INTEGER),
17 0, 0, 0, 0,
18 (X509V3_EXT_I2S)i2s_ASN1_INTEGER,
19 0,
20 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL
21};

23const X509V3_EXT_METHOD v3_delta_crl = {
24 NID_delta_crl, 0, ASN1_ITEM_ref(ASN1_INTEGER),

31static void *s2i_asn1_int(X509V3_EXT_METHOD *meth, X509V3_CTX *ctx,
32 const char *value)
33{
34 return s2i_ASN1_INTEGER(meth, value);
35}

42 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL
43};
